      "english_close": "The subject-matter (viṣaya) of the Vedāntas is Brahman. [This is so] because it is not common to any other source (ananyasādhāraṇatva). And because it is what they expound (tat-pratipādyatva). The relation between Brahman and the Vedāntas is, accordingly, the one characterized as that between what is to be expounded and what expounds it.",
